    <item>
      <title>碧桂园在债务计划下恢复交易，股价大涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/country-garden-to-resume-trading-after-debt-overhaul-progress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[碧桂园控股有限公司承诺就债务重组计划与债权人达成协议，该公司股价周二在停牌九个月后于香港复牌，随后股价大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/country-garden-to-resume-trading-after-debt-overhaul-progress</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 00:43:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普坚持对墨西哥和加拿大征收关税，黄金延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/gold-holds-gain-as-reduced-threat-of-us-trade-war-hurts-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布可能于下个月初对墨西哥和加拿大征收关税，尽管他没有立即对中国征收进口税，但金价小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/gold-holds-gain-as-reduced-threat-of-us-trade-war-hurts-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 00:23:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普暗示将对加拿大征收关税并推动国内能源发展，油价出现波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员消化了唐纳德·特朗普总统的一系列承诺和行政命令，包括对加拿大征收关税的威胁以及提高国内能源产量的计划，油价在涨跌之间摇摆不定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 23:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划对墨西哥、加拿大征收关税，美元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他正考虑从下个月开始对加拿大和墨西哥实施先前威胁的关税，随后美元上涨，亚洲股市一度抹去开盘涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 22:26:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员等待特朗普加密货币行政命令，比特币回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/bitcoin-rises-to-fresh-record-ahead-of-trump-inauguration-in-us-m64q8dma</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普就任美国第 47 任总统后，交易员们正在等待其支持加密货币的政策指示，比特币从历史高点回落。]]></description>
